1292
00:42:48,370 --> 00:42:49,470
Good.

1293
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:52,069
Should we get meat since we have the two here?

1294
00:42:52,070 --> 00:42:53,510
Sounds good.

1295
00:42:53,740 --> 00:42:55,710
Meat sounds very good.

1296
00:42:55,840 --> 00:42:57,309
- We... - Meat sounds good.

1297
