You can smell pulppang.

1330
00:44:10,220 --> 00:44:12,049
Something smells good.

1331
00:44:12,050 --> 00:44:13,820
- I'm hungry. - It smells like pulppang.

1332
00:44:14,790 --> 00:44:16,290
Should I get us some walnut cakes?

1333
