1334
00:44:18,360 --> 00:44:19,660
- Do you have cash? - Yes.

1335
00:44:19,830 --> 00:44:21,099
I'll start snacking...

1336
00:44:21,100 --> 00:44:22,360
- once I eat one. - Right?

1337
00:44:23,000 --> 00:44:24,130
- Exactly. - Have one and...

1338
00:44:24,570 --> 00:44:26,170
I love those peanuts!

1339
00:44:27,170 --> 00:44:28,700
I absolutely love those peanuts.

1340
00:44:28,840 --> 00:44:30,240
- Yes? - How about...

1341
00:44:31,070 --> 00:44:33,170
- We'll take everything. - Gosh.

1342
00:44:33,640 --> 00:44:35,239
- Peanuts. - Okay.

1343
00:44:35,240 --> 00:44:36,610
Nice.

1344
00:44:36,780 --> 00:44:38,150
She's putting them in with a smile.

1345
00:44:40,320 --> 00:44:41,820
- Are you happy? - Yes.

1346
00:44:42,120 --> 00:44:44,820
- She's happy, and so are we. - Everyone is happy.

1347
00:44:45,090 --> 00:44:47,259
- Exactly 11. Nice. - Perfect.

1348
00:44:47,260 --> 00:44:48,389
I wanted to give you more.

1349
00:44:48,390 --> 00:44:49,719
- It's enough. - Don't worry about it.

1350
00:44:49,720 --> 00:44:50,890
- Twenty dollars. - Yes.

1351
00:44:51,260 --> 00:44:53,190
- Twenty dollars. - Thank you.

1352
00:44:54,500 --> 00:44:55,629
Thank you.

1353
00:44:55,630 --> 00:44:57,400
- Happy New Year. - Happy New Year.

1354
00:44:57,600 --> 00:44:58,729
- These peanuts look bomb. - Thank you.

1355
00:44:58,730 --> 00:45:00,299
- Let's dig in. - Okay.

1356
00:45:00,300 --> 00:45:01,740
(Straight up eating the peanut bread)

1357
00:45:02,040 --> 00:45:04,140
I've never had bread filled with so many peanuts.

1358
00:45:05,140 --> 00:45:06,810
- The Chinese place? - Okay.

1359
00:45:07,280 --> 00:45:08,979
- Delicious. - To think we'd decide things...

1360
00:45:08,980 --> 00:45:10,080
right away.

1361
00:45:10,210 --> 00:45:12,079
- Shall I sit in the back? - I'll take the middle seat.

1362
00:45:12,080 --> 00:45:13,409
- Get in. - Hold on.

1363
00:45:13,410 --> 00:45:14,619
- Get in, Sung Hoon. - I'll sit in the middle.

1364
00:45:14,620 --> 00:45:15,719
- I'll sit in the middle. - Here.

1365
00:45:15,720 --> 00:45:17,190
- I'll sit. - No, I'll sit in the middle.

1366
00:45:18,290 --> 00:45:20,659
- Let's put on the seatbelt - Let's put on the seatbelt

1367
00:45:20,660 --> 00:45:21,820
Let's put on the seatbelt

1368
