Sit sideways. That's it.

1371
00:45:27,960 --> 00:45:29,360
- Good. - We have to ride like this.

1372
00:45:29,500 --> 00:45:31,870
- You can't see Sung Hoon. - Your big head is blocking me.

1373
00:45:32,570 --> 00:45:34,370
We all have our shoulders to the side.

1374
00:45:34,570 --> 00:45:36,099
Our shoulders are overlapping.

1375
00:45:36,100 --> 00:45:37,939
The 3 of you in 1 shot are so cute.

1376
00:45:37,940 --> 00:45:40,580
- We're all sitting sideways. - You can't see Sung Hoon.

1377
00:45:40,810 --> 00:45:43,010
- They're all too big. - Seriously.

1378
00:45:43,640 --> 00:45:44,810
I have no space.

1379
00:45:45,180 --> 00:45:48,180
We're practically sitting like an alumni photo.

1380
00:45:48,750 --> 00:45:50,320
Are you on your way after succeeding?

1381
00:45:50,620 --> 00:45:51,819
- No, we failed. - We failed.

1382
00:45:51,820 --> 00:45:53,019
We failed.

1383
00:45:53,020 --> 00:45:54,689
- It just... - We were so close.

1384
00:45:54,690 --> 00:45:56,860
- Really. - You hit the nail on the head.

1385
00:45:57,660 --> 00:45:58,830
We were about to make it.

1386
00:45:59,130 --> 00:46:00,359
I watch Whenever Possible...

1387
00:46:00,360 --> 00:46:01,760
- every now and then. - Is that so?

1388
00:46:02,660 --> 00:46:03,870
It was...

1389
00:46:05,870 --> 00:46:06,870
We're heading to Saejeol Station,

1390
00:46:06,871 --> 00:46:08,070
- right? - Yes.

1391
00:46:09,340 --> 00:46:10,810
It's my sense of direction.

1392
00:46:10,970 --> 00:46:12,839
- I remember going left. - Hey.

1393
00:46:12,840 --> 00:46:14,740
- Listen, Dong Hyun. - Sorry.

1394
00:46:16,280 --> 00:46:18,180
- The driver has a GPS. - I'm sorry.

1395
00:46:18,510 --> 00:46:21,819
My gut is telling me we have to go left...

1396
00:46:21,820 --> 00:46:22,849
to get to Saejeol Station.

1397
00:46:22,850 --> 00:46:24,150
(What gut feeling?)

1398
00:46:24,950 --> 00:46:26,490
- We're here. - Over there.

1399
00:46:26,690 --> 00:46:28,060
It's where the real estate office is.

1400
00:46:28,360 --> 00:46:30,690
- Thank you. - Thank you.

1401
00:46:30,890 --> 00:46:32,860
- Our shoulders were overlapping. - Do succeed.

1402
00:46:33,090 --> 00:46:34,260
- Thank you. - No problem.

1403
00:46:35,500 --> 00:46:36,730
Hold on, it's...

1404
